snippet.title: Annihilator Demo trailer
snippet.description:
A brand new Game Boy Color game coming soon. You can also pre-order the physical and digital game.

Pre-orders start now! Oct. 1-31. 
*ROM is included when ordering physical product.
Expected release date: Q1, 2024
 
Physical: https://ko-fi.com/s/2680a622a4
Digital: https://ko-fi.com/s/fb2ded6ae5
Media Inquiry: https://forms.gle/8Dis9xPx8j3QB1eaA
Old demo: https://saltandpixel.itch.io/crush-gb
